g.text: Offering lot or serial number (if generated for product)
Manufacturer, packager or distributor name (actual corporate name, can include name of a division) or logo4
Manufacturer, packager or distributor address (at least the City, State/Province, zip code and Country) intended as main place
Works in Progress or Limited Market statement if applicable
The word “Sterile” for devices intended to be sold in sterile condition
The method of sterilization, if the device is sterilized
The expiry date of the device, if the device has one.
Indication that device is for single use, as appropriate
Storage or handling conditions, as necessary
Details necessary on the packaging label to identify the device and contents of the package
The words ‘custom-made device’ if the device is custom-made
Copyright, trademark, patent protection and other legal statements (e.g., privacy policy)
Installation, set-up and maintenance information (not for software)
New features and functionality introduced in the release
List of notable defects resolved in the release
cant outstanding defects known to be in the release that the customer should be made aware of
